stories.text:
Hi everybody! Due to Covid 19 pandemic I was forced in my home, so I revamped my book

https://8bit.gioorgi.com

It is a huge collection of information about the 8bit comnputer era (1980-1985) up to the NES console. I collected information from various source including “The 8bit Guy” videos and specific site (like C64 wiki, nesdev etc).

I am using docusaurus to give a pleasnt look to the whole site.

Please give me you feedback (and happy new year btw)!

stories.text:
I have an open source project hosted at https://github.com/zinggAI/zingg/.

In the traffic section of a repository, I see the referring sites and the number of views and unique visitors. I am curious if this data is for 14 days like the git clones or visitors or is there some other time frame here? I could not find anything in the documentation that talks about this. Can someone please let me know ?
